Package: ftserussell.com
Title: FTSE Russell Index Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for FTSE Russell index data. Covers Russell
    index values (YTD and historical) and FTSE historic index values. Includes
    LLM context injection via ftse_context().
